==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Criticalness
<hw>Crit"ic*al*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The state or
quality of being critical, or of occurring at a critical time.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Accuracy in examination or decision;
exactness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>critical point</ent>⟦br⟧
